;
SHEET
DETERMINATION METHOD: DSSP
THE SHEETS PRESENTED AS "AB" AND "BB" IN EACH CHAIN ON SHEET RECORDS
BELOW ARE ACTUALLY 8-STRANDED BARRELS THAT ARE REPRESENTED BY
9-STRANDED SHEETS IN WHICH THE FIRST AND LAST STRANDS
ARE IDENTICAL.
;
